{"tid":909332,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[痴撚線］頭先個細路問公仔麵點解冇公仔 我答唔出俾人屌","createTime":"2018-11-20T10:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T11:17:49.000Z","uid":53023,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff521492eba8b92c9c90b47393359b7926dc717","tid":909332,"uid":53023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T10:10:28.000Z","msg":"我係做茶餐廳嘅<br />\n <br />\n頭先有個細路叫咗碟豬扒炒公仔麵<br />\n<br />\n碟麵好撚香 拎咗俾佢之後佢問我公仔呢<br />\n<br />\n我就話：公仔麵冇公仔嘅喎 你媽媽冇教你咩？<br />\n<br />\n佢老母答唔出 跟住屌鳩我：咪係囉 你做侍應點解唔知呀<br />\n<br />\n佢老母應該25歲左右，好撚大波（目測有e) 九成都係俾人<br />\n<br />\n中出即飛嘅mk妹（小露波gap,同我嘅對話有幾分淫賤）<br />\n<br />\n示意圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PEbVbSJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPEbVbSJ.png&h=dd78c7c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ikcJkL5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FikcJkL5.png&h=5435044c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hYJ8wSM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhYJ8wSM.png&h=bc97d1e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jis5y57.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjis5y57.png&h=14b4fc33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rupzsq9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRupzsq9.png&h=117e56b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想即刻打個丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99f6d305d70b806ad10a7c34b915d9b8ea96759","tid":909332,"uid":11055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T10:35:33.000Z","msg":"點解會係有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5aff0a1b019271041f2efa54f0e7ba11fa99b0","tid":909332,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T10:36:57.000Z","msg":"圖文不符 負皮"},{"pid":"ba9eaac767ab